{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>General Description</strong></h2><br>Fear Of The Darkness is a narrative psychological horror game that will push you to face the serious phobias of some patients.<br><br>Play as the enigmatic doctor in charge of treating them, or at least try, it won't be an easy mission.<br><br>Avoid by all means being overwhelmed by the heavy emotional burden of your patients, come out of the Darkness and explore the various corners of the so-called Truth.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793200/extras/Doctor_home.jpg?t=1730110378\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Setting</strong></h2><br>The main environment of the game is a strange room, where everything changes often, a bit like it is in our nature.<br><br>Be careful, here you will be able to discover many details about the characters' stories after delving into their minds; you will be able to unlock new powers, relax, look around and continue this unusual journey.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793200/extras/room.jpg?t=1730110378\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2>Go through the different phases of the game and rummages through the patients' rarefied memories, always in search of Clarity.<br><br>Explore these 4 intriguing stories, each with its own unique gameplay:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> a platform phase in which you will have to jump carefully to reach the end of the various paths, but remember that nothing lasts forever...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793200/extras/Nathan_2_rid.jpg?t=1730110378\" /><br><br></li><li> a phase where you will encounter something or someone in the dark that is not real, or maybe it is?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793200/extras/Sarah_2_rid.jpg?t=1730110378\" /><br><br></li><li> a fast-paced phase in which you will be encouraged to run and escape, but escape from what?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793200/extras/Tim_2_rid.jpg?t=1730110378\" /><br><br></li><li> a puzzle phase where you will have to use your skills to get to the goal, or perhaps you will prefer to linger for a long time?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793200/extras/Lucas_2_rid.jpg?t=1730110378\" /></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Final Advice</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Clarity could help you...</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793200/extras/Light_rid.jpg?t=1730110378\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Nathan?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1793200/0fe22b86a00f4478e2dfa1ede1f92142692b4ee0.jpg"},{"name":"Sarah?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1793200/15165ce26aa0982b52db3a4350ad80a9738f1520.jpg"},{"name":"Tim?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1793200/4961ffd59d5ea3fcb4c6874a19491406257966d5.jpg"},{"name":"Lucas?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1793200/dca4b4915d842163004794942c09e2ba5e780910.jpg"},{"name":"Acrophobia?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1793200/5a7deb19b51a528b432c833a670004fdb2b6b934.jpg"},{"name":"Phasmophobia?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1793200/7b640f7d78bfa2f7ed65f118299f99469f7fb24f.jpg"},{"name":"Claustrophobia?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1793200/25829485b9832b1404bd43dbb42df51af9c5449a.jpg"},{"name":"Abandoned?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic